                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200517-30-off175 t18200517-30-cd176"></join>, one coat, value 10 s.; one waistcoat, value 2 s.; one pair of breeches, value 5 s.; one shirt, value 2 s.; eight crown pieces and four half-crowns, the goods and monies of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18200517-30-victim316" type="victimName">
